{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"4232","heading":"Low-income requirement and income targeting","label":"4232 Low-income requirement and income targeting","identifier":"/us/usc/t25/s4232","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t25/ch43/schVIII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft25%2Fs4232","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Codification, and , enacted identical sections 813 of . This section is based on the text of , as added by .Pub. L. 106–568, § 203Pub. L. 106–569, § 513Pub. L. 104–330section 813 of Pub. L. 104–330Pub. L. 106–569, § 513"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t25/s4232/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t25/s4232","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft25%2Fs4232%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t25/s4232/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t25/s4232/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft25%2Fs4232%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t25/s4232/a/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t25/s4232/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft25%2Fs4232%2Fa%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"in the case of rental housing, is made available for occupancy only by a family that is a low-income family at the time of the initial occupancy of that family of that unit; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"